=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /wεəɻ/

=== Verb ===
'''to wear''' ([[wore]], [[worn]])

# to [[put]] on an item of [[clothing]]
# to [[tire]] out.
#{{nautical}} To bring a [[sailing]] [[ship]] onto the other [[tack]] by bringing the [[wind]] around the [[stern]] (as opposed to [[tacking]] when the wind is brought around the [[bow]])

